question: Which restaurant can I find along the route to Wellington Reservation, Wellington, OH within 180 kilometers from Go Ape Treetop Adventure Course, Strongsville, OH?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.818381 41.322133)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-82.231694 41.147108)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.818381 41.322133)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.818381 41.322133)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Cake Walk Indian Restaurant and Bakery
The Old Bag of Nails Pub
Kabuki Korean Restaurant and Sushi Bar

[3].display_name: Go Ape Treetop Adventure Course, Strongsville, OH
